## Disclaimer

This Draft Red Herring Prospectus is issued by Parag Milk Foods Limited for the purpose of inviting offers for subscription of Equity Shares. This Draft Red Herring Prospectus does not constitute an offer or invitation to subscribe for or purchase Equity Shares. The Equity Shares may or may not be allotted. The decision to allot Equity Shares shall be taken by the Board of Directors of Parag Milk Foods Limited in consultation with the BRLMs.

The investors are advised to read this Draft Red Herring Prospectus carefully before investing in the Equity Shares. The investors are also advised to consult their own financial, legal and tax advisors before investing in the Equity Shares.

Parag Milk Foods Limited and the BRLMs do not accept any liability for any loss or damage arising out of or in connection with this Draft Red Herring Prospectus.

